        "title": "IN THE CELLAR",
        "video-sec-content-txt-1": "<p>In the Alvi’s Drift cellar, our winemaking team strongly focuses on preserving the fruit-driven expression of the grapes that go into our award-winning South African wines.</p><p>Only the best-quality, free-run juice was used to produce this unique Chenin Blanc – a truly one-of-a-kind wine unlike any other produced in our cellar. A blend of barrel-matured and fresh, crisp tank-fermented Chenin Blanc; 20-30% of this wine was fermented and aged in French oak barrels, with the balance fermented in stainless steel tanks.</p>",
